description: SELLER OFFERING ALLOWANCE TOWARD 2:1 RATE BUYDOWN. Intown city-living with resort style amenities awaits you at PLAZA MIDTOWN consisting of two high-rise condominium buildings (each 20 stories high) in Midtown Atlanta on the corner of W. Peachtree Street and Peachtree Place. Location is key with direct elevator access downstairs to Publix and easy walkability to restaurants, shopping, Atlanta Beltline, Piedmont Park, Marta, GA Tech, NCR Corporation, PWC, and Alston & Bird. Located in the East Plaza Midtown building above W. Peachtree, this furnished condo is move-in ready with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in a roommate style floor plan. The floor-to-ceiling windows provides a city view from all rooms. Entertain guests in the open-concept kitchen at the kitchen island, dining area and living room. The stylish kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash and sleek dark cabinets. The primary bedroom suite offers a view of mesmerizing city lights and an ensuite bathroom with double sinks, shower with large soaking tub, and stone tile flooring leading to a sizable custom walk-in closet. The condo is offered furnished and includes a stackable washer/dryer, a coveted STORAGE UNIT (10'x5'), and an assigned, secure parking space. East Plaza Midtown has an impressive lobby entrance with 24-hour concierge and security. The amazing amenities include the resort-style POOL with all day sun, GYM, and CLUBROOM available to residents for private gatherings. Excellent walkability or quick scooter ride to the Fox Theatre, Mercedes Benz Stadium, Phillips Arena, Centennial Park, Atlantic Station, Ponce City Market and many other popular Atlanta sites.
